OL,7,FAn independent Scotland would allow
OL,8,Fpeople born overseas to automatically
OL,9,Fclaim citizenship if one of their
OL,10,Fparents was Scottish, under plans due
OL,11,Fto be announced on Thursday.
OL,13,FThe policy will form a key part of
OL,14,Fthe latest Scottish Government
OL,15,Fprospectus paper on independence,
OL,16,Fwhich is on the subject of
OL,17,Fcitizenship.
OL,3,CPeople with Scottish parents could
OL,4,Capply for citizenship if country
OL,5,Cvotes for independence
